---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import CTAButton from '../../../components/CTAButton.astro';
import { COMPANY_INFO } from '../../../utils/constants';

const lang = 'ms';
const post = {
  title: 'Isuzu vs Fuso Lori 2026 - Pembiayaan 0% Deposit',
  slug: 'isuzu-vs-fuso-lori-2026-bandingan',
  excerpt: 'Bandingan Isuzu vs Fuso lori 2026. Isuzu Giga RM90,000+, Fuso Fighter RM85,000+. Bank minta 10-20% deposit. Ing Heng tawarkan 0% deposit untuk kedua-dua jenama. Dapatkan kelulusan 24-48 jam.',
  date: '2026-01-08',
  author: 'Pasukan Ing Heng Credit',
  readTime: 5,
  category: 'Pembiayaan Jentera',
  image: '/images/blog/isuzu-vs-fuso.jpg'
};

const keywords = ['pembiayaan jentera', 'isuzu', 'fuso', 'lori', '0% deposit'];
const breadcrumbItems = [
  { label: 'Utama', href: '/ms' },
  { label: 'Blog', href: '/ms/blog' },
  { label: post.title, href: `/ms/blog/${post.slug}` }
];
---

<BaseLayout title={post.title} description={post.excerpt} lang={lang} keywords={keywords}>
  <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "BlogPosting",
      "headline": post.title,
      "description": post.excerpt,
      "datePublished": post.date,
      "author": { "@type": "Organization", "name": post.author },
      "publisher": {
        "@type": "Organization",
        "name": "Ing Heng Credit & Leasing Sdn Bhd",
        "logo": {
          "@type": "ImageObject",
          "url": "https://inghengcredit.com/logo.png"
        }
      }
    }
  </script>

  <Breadcrumbs items={breadcrumbItems} />

  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <header class="mb-8">
      <span class="text-sm font-semibold" style="color: #D4A574;">Pembiayaan Jentera</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mt-2" style="color: #2D1810; font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase;">{post.title}</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">{post.excerpt}</p>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4">
        <span>{post.author}</span>
        <span>•</span>
        <time>{new Date(post.date).toLocaleDateString('ms-MY', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</time>
        <span>•</span>
        <span>{post.readTime} min bacaan</span>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h2>Isuzu vs Fuso: Mana Satu Lebih Baik?</h2>

      <p>Dua jenama lori paling popular di Malaysia: Isuzu dan Fuso. Kedua-duanya mempunyai kelebihan tersendiri. Tetapi bank sangat ketat untuk pembiayaan kedua-dua jenama ini.</p>

      <h2>Isuzu Giga Series</h2>

      <p>Isuzu Giga adalah pilihan popular untuk lori 5-tan dan 10-tan:</p>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Harga:</strong> RM90,000 - RM140,000</li>
        <li><strong>Enjin:</strong> 6HK1 diesel, 300HP</li>
        <li><strong>Kelebihan:</strong> Jimat minyak, tahan lama</li>
        <li><strong>Kegunaan:</strong> Pengangkutan barang, perkhidmatan</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Fuso Fighter Series</h2>

      <p>Fuso Fighter adalah pesaing kuat untuk Isuzu:</p>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Harga:</strong> RM85,000 - RM130,000</li>
        <li><strong>Enjin:</strong> 6M60 diesel, 270HP</li>
        <li><strong>Kelebihan:</strong> Kuasa tinggi, harga berpatutan</li>
        <li><strong>Kegunaan:</strong> Pembinaan, pengangkutan</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Bank vs Ing Heng: Pembiayaan</h2>

      <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 2rem 0;">
        <thead>
          <tr style="background: #2D1810; color: white;">
            <th style="padding: 1rem; text-align: left;">Ciri-ciri</th>
            <th style="padding: 1rem; text-align: center;">Bank</th>
            <th style="padding: 1rem; text-align: center;">Ing Heng</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">
            <td style="padding: 1rem;"><strong>Down Payment</strong></td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; text-align: center; color: #dc2626;">10-20%</td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; text-align: center; color: #16a34a;"><strong>0%</strong></td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; background: #f9fafb;">
            <td style="padding: 1rem;"><strong>Pinjaman</strong></td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; text-align: center;">90%</td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; text-align: center;"><strong>100%</strong></td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">
            <td style="padding: 1rem;"><strong>Had Umur</strong></td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; text-align: center; color: #dc2626;">5 tahun</td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; text-align: center; color: #16a34a;"><strong>Tiada had</strong></td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; background: #f9fafb;">
            <td style="padding: 1rem;"><strong>Kelulusan</strong></td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; text-align: center;">2-4 minggu</td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; text-align: center;"><strong>24-48 jam</strong></td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <h2>Contoh: Isuzu Giga RM100,000</h2>

      <p><strong>Bank:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Deposit (10%): RM10,000</li>
        <li>Pinjaman: RM90,000</li>
        <li>Had umur: 5 tahun maksimum</li>
      </ul>

      <p><strong>Ing Heng:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Deposit (0%): <strong>RM0</strong></li>
        <li>Pinjaman: <strong>RM100,000</strong></li>
        <li>Had umur: Tiada had</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Hubungi Kami Hari Ini</h2>

      <p>Dapatkan pembiayaan Isuzu atau Fuso 0% deposit dengan Ing Heng.</p>

      <div style="background: #F5F0E8; border-left: 4px solid #D4A574; padding: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0;">
        <h3 style="color: #2D1810; margin-top: 0;">Isuzu atau Fuso?</h3>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">Dapatkan kelulusan pembiayaan 0% deposit untuk kedua-dua jenama dalam 24-48 jam. WhatsApp kami untuk konsultasi percuma.</p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 0;"><strong>Hubungi:</strong> +60175700889 (WhatsApp) | 03-3324 8899 (Telefon)</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t">
      <CTAButton text="Dapatkan Pembiayaan Lori" link={COMPANY_INFO.whatsapp.link} variant="accent" size="large" />
    </footer>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  h2 {
    color: #2D1810;
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 3px solid #D4A574;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  h3 {
    color: #8B6F47;
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  p {
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #374151;
  }

  strong {
    color: #2D1810;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding-left: 0;
  }

  li {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #374151;
  }

  li::before {
    content: '✓';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #D4A574;
    font-weight: bold;
  }
</style>
